text: Carolyn Laurie "Carol" Kane (born June 18, 1952) is an American actress. On television, she won an Emmy Award for her acting on the series Taxi. She has been in many movies including Annie Hall, Jumpin' Jack Flash and The Princess Bride. On Broadway, she worked on the musical Wicked.
